WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:02.278
Previously on Royal Pains...

00:05.334 --> 00:07.083
No, Divya's taking care
of me, so...

00:07.085 --> 00:09.135
you called six times to tell me

00:09.137 --> 00:10.420
you're drunk with Divya?

00:10.422 --> 00:11.921
No, of course not.
Divya's pregnant.

00:11.923 --> 00:14.424
She's not drinking
I am officially homeless.

00:14.426 --> 00:17.894
You could stay at my house.

00:17.896 --> 00:21.848
I got you these.

00:21.850 --> 00:23.966
- Thanks.
- Flak pills.

00:23.968 --> 00:26.069
- Ow! Ow! Ow.
- All right, stop, stop, stop.

00:26.071 --> 00:28.905
Can you give her something
for the pain?

00:28.907 --> 00:30.857
Molly, take one
of these hydrocodone.

00:30.859 --> 00:32.192
It'll help.
Turn around.

00:32.194 --> 00:34.361
Whoa, Molly! Molly!

00:36.615 --> 00:38.031
Dad?
Dad?

00:38.033 --> 00:40.083
The police want you to submit
to a tox screen.

00:40.085 --> 00:41.785
And I told them that wouldn't
be a problem.

00:41.787 --> 00:45.021
It isn't a problem, is it?
Of course not.

